## Typography

I wanted to look just different enough. Current typographical trends are often very endemic to a certain vocabulary. I wanted something inbetween. So I decided to go with a combination of “Work Sans” for heavy but warm headlines and “Poppins” for geometric and pleasent paragraphs. Luckily Google Fonts provides Work Sans as a variable font and includes many open type features.

