## Illustration & Icons

My drawing skills have rusted since I stopped drawing. But I still like to “illustrate” (lol) with abstract shapes. I loved the idea of using simple shapes that remind of toy building blocks to create abstract compositions.

Later on I decided to also play with different patterns and for a short amount of time, some of the illustrations even served as quasi diagrams.

